<h2 class = "firmy">Our Firm</h2>
<figure>
<img class = "firm" src = "images/te.jpg" width = "410" height="255">

<figcaption>MJS Accounting group is the premier accounting group in the 
Tampa Bay Metro Area. For over a decade, we have provided for the accounting 
needs of all types of businesses and individual clients. From mom and pop 
businesses to mutli-million dollar corporations, we apply our personal touch 
to your financial situation. As part of your business team, our primary goal for
 you is to be successful. We work for you. Our clients return year after year because 
 we deliver value and recognized results. 

</br></br>
We take pride in educating and empowering our clients. 
We recognize that no two people or businesses are alike, and we 
encourage you to choose services that fit your needs.  We provide 
accurate, timely information to help you make solid business decisions.
 We are approachable and available when you need us. 

</br></br>
We offer tax planning and preparation, monthly bookkeeping and reconciliation, financial statements, weekly payroll processing, accounting software implementation, IRS audit representation and more! 

</br></br>
Look for our informative webinars which will enlighten you on a variety of topics such as which type of corporation is right for your business  and the advantages of a Roth IRA vs. Traditional IRA.



