 <h2 class = "firmy">Senior Accountant</h2>
<figure>
<img class ="Nadeen" src = "images/NADEEN.jpg" width="210" height="210">
<figcaption>Nadeen S. Buchalter is the President and CEO of MJS Accounting Group.
Nadeen graduated from New York University in 1987 with a Bachelor of Science degree in Accounting and Finance.  She worked for over 20 years in the accounting field preparing taxes before founding MJS Accounting Group in 2008.
 
Nadeen has an extensive background in both business and personal tax matters. She is a strong believer in educating her clients and providing unconditional support.  She has taught accounting at the local college as well as to small businesses owners through interactive seminars.
 
Nadeen in an Enrolled Agent and certified QuickBooks Pro Advisor
She is a member in good standing of the AICPA and FICPA.
</figcaption>
